# Weather Forecast API with LangChain 🌦️

This project uses **LangChain** to integrate **Open-Meteo API** and **Nominatim API** to provide weather forecasts for cities in **Pakistan**. The tool allows users to input a city name and returns the **current temperature** and **wind speed**.

## **Features**
- Retrieve real-time weather information using **Open-Meteo API**.
- Convert city names to coordinates using **Nominatim API**.
- Handle API failures and user input errors gracefully.
